{"tid":1637620,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【爭最佳外語片】《哪吒》代表強國出戰奧斯卡 93地電影爭最後10強","createTime":"2019-10-08T04:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T06:26:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ef63d2785227965bd2c8339a973a2c081cd62b48","tid":1637620,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"第92屆奧斯卡頒獎禮將於明年2月舉行，奧斯卡金像獎主辦單位、美國電影藝術與科學學院（AMPAS）今日正式公佈有份角逐最佳外語片的海外作品名單，今屆共有93個國家、地區之電影合資格爭獎，日本動畫大師新海誠力作《天氣之子》代表日本出戰，與韓國名導奉俊昊執導、宋康昊主演的韓片《上流寄生族》同屬名單之列。<br />\n台灣則有徐譽庭、許智彥執導的《誰先愛上他的》，由邱澤夥拍金馬影后謝盈萱合作，而香港代表是邱禮濤執導、劉德華及古天樂主演的《掃毒2天地對決》。至於勁收逾48億人民幣的大陸動畫《哪吒之魔童降世》，就成為13億人的希望。泰國方面，今年4月在港上映的《飛人類之吻》成功出線有望衝奧。<br />\n奧斯卡大會將於12月16日揭曉最後10強，明年1月中正式公佈各提名名單，2月9日舉行頒獎禮。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191008/large/1570508319_c004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191008%2Flarge%2F1570508319_c004.jpg&h=56687662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191008/60129193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60129193&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnImqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=e171124d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60129193&h=e9dbabf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191008/60129193</a>"},{"pid":"55b1c55ed31f955ea59d6842978e0abee94a5ee3","tid":1637620,"uid":308567,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:58:50.000Z","msg":"隻哪吒個樣好撚中国<br />\n<br />\n又樣衰 又周圍屙尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1017c8e6d444eb7cd1dbd44471d78a05299c7f0f","tid":1637620,"uid":60500,"like":1,"disli